Thika Knut has accused the TSC of underhand dealings in the ongoing teachers promotion drive.Yesterday, Thika Knut branch executive secretary general Joe Mungai said some of those who did not apply for promotions have received letters inviting them for interviews.A Kiambu TSC official, who spoke on condition of anonymity, said they are receiving the invitation letters from the headquarters.More than 400 teachers applied for the promotions in Gatanga, Thika, Ruiru and Juja subcounties.